transcripts.text: Donald Trump has made it clear he's got Joe Biden on his mind because Trump knows Biden will beat him in Pennsylvania, Michigan, and Wisconsin, the states we need to take back the presidency.  Joe Biden stood on the world stage, helped make Obamacare the law of the land, and can step in on day one.  It's why Trump can't stop talking about Joe Biden.
I'm Joe Biden, and I approve this message.
